title: LF Silver Duo Partner! TOP/JG main (Fine with anywhere though)

embed.description: Check your Summoner statistics, MMR, realtime spectate and using powerful global LoL Charts!

body:
Hey guys, just looking for a duo partner to play with, maybe a new addition to my group of friends who play together.
Been in a bit of a rut past coupe games, mostly due to me being on some mad tilt. Hoping to get out of it with a reliable duo partner.

Feel free to add me - OhMyGawdzilla
